    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, though all electronics and the air conditioning are still working as they should. Mechanically, the car runs and drives fine, though it does have a slow oil seep and will likely need new brake pads in the coming months. It has been regularly serviced, and I have the records available for your review.",
      "price": 24500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of reliability and refinement with this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle. Each component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and performance. This car offers a smooth, confident drive and an interior that reflects a history of careful stewardship. We pride ourselves on offering high-caliber vehicles that provide our clients with long-term value and absolute peace of mind. Secure a premium driving experience today.",
      "price": 32450.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my favorite set of wheels. This car has been an absolute joy to own\u2014it\u2019s that rare kind of ride that still puts a smile on my face every time I turn the key. It\u2019s been kept in lovely condition and runs like a dream; honestly, it feels like it\u2019s just getting started! Sure, you might find a tiny little nudge or a faint mark if you\u2019re looking for them, but to me, those are just signs of a car that\u2019s been loved and driven. It\u2019s been well-maintained and is ready for many more adventures. Why don't you swing by, we'll grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself how sweet this ride really is?",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This machine is a masterclass in mechanical synergy, featuring a meticulously tuned forced-induction powerplant with optimized thermal management for consistent peak boost. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from revised suspension geometry and high-durometer bushings that sharpen turn-in response. Power is delivered through a precision-balanced drivetrain with a limited-slip differential that ensures maximum traction during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Every service interval has been treated as a critical system check, utilizing high-shear synthetic lubricants to maintain tight internal tolerances. The cockpit provides a tactile connection to the road, with a short-throw shifter that offers crisp, mechanical engagement. Dialed in for the enthusiast who demands linear power and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 38950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs perfect. Clean title. Zero issues. Best deal on the market. Won't last.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a legacy of elegance and adventure. This classic grand tourer doesn't just transport you; it transforms every journey into a cinematic experience. Feel the weight of the steering wheel as it connects you to the road with a tactile honesty missing from modern machines. The engine breathes with a deep, reassuring resonance, a testament to an era when cars were built to be felt, not just driven. Its finish catches the light with a warmth that only years of careful stewardship can provide, while the interior offers a sanctuary of rich textures and timeless design. This is a vehicle for the dreamer, the collector of moments who understands that true beauty lies in a car that has lived, breathed, and is ready to do it all over again with you at the helm.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a masterfully maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This car has been curated for the driver who demands quality, featuring a documented history of care and a comprehensive inspection to ensure peak mechanical performance. The cabin environment is remarkably preserved, offering a premium experience that reflects the vehicle's history of responsible ownership. Secure a vehicle that offers the ideal synthesis of longevity and value\u2014a truly dependable choice for your next investment.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally letting go of my pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s been an absolute dream. This beauty has been my reliable companion for weekend getaways and local cruises alike. She\u2019s got a few tiny character marks here and there\u2014just the usual signs of a life well-lived\u2014but she runs smooth as silk and still turns heads at every stoplight. I\u2019ve always made sure she got plenty of TLC and regular maintenance. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s ready to hit the open road today with a smile, you\u2019ve found it. Come by for a chat and a test drive; I\u2019d love to see her go to a neighbor who will appreciate her as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for grabs is a meticulously sorted performance machine featuring a 3.0L twin-scroll powerplant with rock-solid compression across all cylinders. I\u2019ve focused on sharpening the turn-in response with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a dialed-in dampening profile that eliminates any hint of body roll. The ZF-sourced transmission benefits from proactive fluid service, ensuring crisp, rev-matched downshifts and zero slippage under load. Recent top-tier preventative maintenance includes a high-flow cooling system overhaul and precision-torqued subframe bolts. This isn't just a daily driver; it's a mechanically sound platform optimized for high-lateral Gs and linear power delivery. Turn-key and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
